    skos:editorialNote "Definition adapted from Strengholt (Data Management at Scale), pp. 369–371."@en ;
    dp:embedding_note "Business user has source Strengholt, Piethein. Data Management at Scale: Modern Data Architecture with Data Mesh and Data Fabric. O’Reilly Media (Kindle Edition), pp. 369–371."@en .

